{"tid":1340253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好搞元朗警察宿舍","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:49.000Z","uid":276382,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c2b89b25ee3eaef333eda0aec99469ccd9f1c8","tid":1340253,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀報警cut人線<br />\n到左又放撚走曬啲白衫<br />\n圍撚住啲黑衫<br />\n呢啲柒事一定唔可以比班警賊嘅仔女知道<br />\n大家千祈唔好去佢地宿舍門口<br />\n而且佢地宿舍對面有學校<br />\n雖然放緊暑假 但係band 1學校點會唔補課<br />\n唔好阻住人上堂呀<br />\n好多警賊嘅仔女都係嗰兩間地區名校讀書架<br />\n搞親佢地 搞到人地讀唔到大學就唔好啦<br />\n千祈唔好比佢地啲同學知道佢地有咁嘅老豆呀<br />\n唔想見到校園欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8d0c258657d0c980a0c7d55f648248c0daebc2","tid":1340253,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8876b93509519eaf78a8e9c5d28c9953213027f1","tid":1340253,"uid":285030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"仆街黑警"},{"pid":"6639d0196aa7bf9cb2507b760f64ed23093d67f2","tid":1340253,"uid":271867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"79d1b00403eac42d0867aa6127c1302ce2c982c3","tid":1340253,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6cff48e399987657fcf56d52fbf6e9c9f53bde","tid":1340253,"uid":278419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e89bfecc383db4de0f484f58f410bc8b771d732","tid":1340253,"uid":199858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"推爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif